description: Reserved matters application seeking approval of Appearance, Landscaping, Layout and Scale in relation to Phase 1a for the erection of 58 houses comprising 39 x 3 bed houses and 19 x 4 bed houses at Millbrook Park (Inglis Barracks) submitted to meet the requirements of Condition 5 of outline planning application H/04017/09 dated 22 September 2011.
